{"tid":493691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《壹週刊》交易又延期　傳黃浩背後金主曹貴子陷謎網風暴","createTime":"2017-12-08T18:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T18:47:55.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"47bd9c2ae0d7c94c22f3f479f617629759901e9b","tid":493691,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:05:50.000Z","msg":"媒（282），出售旗下《壹週刊》予商人黃浩一事再起波折，經訂約方進一步磋商，雙方簽署文件同意，把交易日期延至明年2月28日。<br />\n<br />\n自8月底公布出售《壹週刊》予黃浩的方案後，完成交易的日期已數度延後，先在9月28日宣布，由原定的10月5日延至同月31日，另加2,000萬保證金，至限期屆滿當日，仍未見完成交易，當時黃浩稱待賣方下周公布情況。至上月7日，壹傳媒再公布接獲買方通知，希望將交易完成日期延至同月21日，期間黃浩曾稱交易或一分為二進行。不過壹傳媒在21日的公告指，這只是買賣雙方當初磋商時的其中一個選項，而該公告亦表明，限期屆滿前並沒有收到買方的通知，因此交易並無完成，且正尋求法律意見，稱交易未必一定可以進行。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，外界一直有傳，黃浩的幕後金主，為近日捲入細價股「謎網風暴」的康健國際主席曹貴子，今年7月黃浩賣《都市日報》，亦有傳是曹貴子以不同的控股公司「左手交右手」，而今期《壹週刊》的封面，正是「曹貴子困境 追蹤細價股死亡名單」，更引述其昔日好友、「玩具大王」蔡志明斥其招搖撞騙。<br />\n<br />\n（圖片來源：《壹週刊》fb及《壹週Plus》）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.post852.com/237273/《壹週刊》交易又延期%E3%80%80傳黃浩背後金主曹貴子陷/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F237273%2F%E3%80%8A%E5%A3%B9%E9%80%B1%E5%88%8A%E3%80%8B%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%8F%88%E5%BB%B6%E6%9C%9F%25E3%2580%2580%E5%82%B3%E9%BB%83%E6%B5%A9%E8%83%8C%E5%BE%8C%E9%87%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%9B%B9%E8%B2%B4%E5%AD%90%E9%99%B7%2F&d=l4n5bHCFn6JX4ua1sAVs%2FIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=6738a8c3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.post852.com/237273/《壹週刊》交易又延期%E3%80%80傳黃浩背後金主曹貴子陷/</a>"},{"pid":"04f7db73987052d42f75d6450b6909bdb3c3d9a0","tid":493691,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:46:16.000Z","msg":"有冇落定先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce27b7ed0b6c0946b1884737e397c2740b9c98c3","tid":493691,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:46:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇<strong>再</strong>落定先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"67858afa109272517f772e1d98c9a4d86e231a1a","tid":493691,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:47:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇<strong>再</strong>落定先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曹貴子可能要賣左天賦海灣先有錢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4338d8bab3bec1cf207ae142c3037072e6218ad3","tid":493691,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:47:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇<strong>再</strong>落定先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曹貴子可能要賣左天賦海灣先有錢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但有錢都留返請大狀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}